parameters: \nc<>You did it, right? You did it--!! Kyaa~!
\nc<>Cashew Nut, please be quiet for a moment.

\nc<>Yes...! You did it, senpai! My eyes weren't wrong after
all!

\nc<>Mmm... Aren't you happy? You can raise your voice even
more, you know?

\nc<>Well, how should I put it... When we talked in the illusion,
they didn't seem like such a bad person.
\nc<>I wonder if there wasn't any other way.

\nc<>There's no need to worry then. This is like a kind of
natural phenomenon.

\nc<>They should appear somewhere in the world again in a few
decades if they don't have self-awareness.

\nc<>I have mixed feelings about that... But, I guess this
settles one matter.

\nc<>Originally, you came here to be cautious of that species,
right? So, what are you going to do from now on?

\nc<>That's right, that villain! Hurry up and go back to your
original world-- mmmmm!!
\nc<>Cashew Nut? Let's have a proper conversation later, okay?

\nc<>Well, that's right. Even though I may not look like it, I
am the queen.

\nc<>Demons staying in this world for a long time without any
contracts or reasons is definitely not good.

\nc<>Anyway, those succubi will continue to live on their own
even if left alone. It's like they can do whatever they want
as long as they have a reason.

\nc<>If Senpai has something to ask of me, I can't say that I
wouldn't listen.

\nc<>I have decided that I will continue to be a magical girl
from now on.

\nc<>At first, I thought this path was tough and painful, and I
wanted to quit. But in the end, it feels like there's no
other path for me.
\nc<>So... will you become my sidekick again?
\nc<>That's unfortunate, Senpai. I can't fulfill that request.
\nc<>I have been your partner from the beginning, Senpai!
